1. On je ubio* Äoveka. (He killed a man.)
2. Ono se ubacuje* u sistem. (It is inserted into the system.)
3. Oni su ubijeni* nogom. (They were killed with a kick.)
4. Ubila* ga je ljubav. (Love killed him.)
5. Ljudi su ubijeni* uzalud. (People were killed in vain.)
6. Oni su ubili* mnoge ljude. (They killed many people.)
7. Ubijanje* je zabranjeno. (Killing is forbidden.)
8. Ona je ubila* sebe. (She killed herself.)